OL,3,CPolice end searches at Andrew
OL,4,CMountbatten-Windsor's former Royal
OL,5,CLodge home
OL,7,FSearches at Andrew Mountbatten-
OL,8,FWindsor's former home, Royal Lodge,
OL,9,Fhave now ended, Thames Valley Police
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FIt follows the former prince's arrest
OL,13,Fon Thursday on suspicion of misconduct
OL,14,Fin public office.
OL,16,FHe spent 11 hours in custody on his
OL,17,F66th birthday, before being released
OL,18,Fon bail, after allegations he shared
OL,19,Fsensitive information with Jeffrey
OL,20,FEpstein during his time as the UK's
OL,21,Ftrade envoy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
