OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772010304
OL,3,CPolice end searches at Andrew
OL,4,CMountbatten-Windsor's former Royal
OL,5,CLodge home
OL,7,FDetectives continued to search his
OL,8,Fformer home in Windsor, Berkshire,
OL,9,Fover the weekend and into Monday.
OL,11,FThames Valley Police said in a
OL,12,Fstatement on Tuesday evening that
OL,13,Fthose searches had now ended.
OL,15,FAssistant Chief Constable Oliver
OL,16,FWright said: "Officers have now left
OL,17,Fthe location we have been searching in
OL,18,FBerkshire. This concludes the search
OL,19,Factivity that commenced following our
OL,20,Farrest of a man in his sixties from
OL,21,FNorfolk on Thursday.
OL,26,@xD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
