OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"We understand the significant public
OL,13,Finterest in this case and our
OL,14,Finvestigation remains ongoing.
OL,16,F"It is important that our
OL,17,Finvestigators are given the time and
OL,18,Fspace to progress their work. We will
OL,19,Fprovide updates when it is appropriate
OL,20,Fto do so, but this is unlikely to be
OL,21,Ffor some time."
